Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}無災無奈的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:09.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}為了打發時間聽收音機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:11.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}從中聽到了那句話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:14.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}非常遺憾 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:16.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}今天地球就要走向終結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:18.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}在不知哪國的總統
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}嗚咽著演說之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}窗外的大鳥們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:54.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}覆蓋住整片天空難以前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:58.34,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}吞沒了新月 向著未知之地驅趕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:01.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}玩到一半的遊戲還沒存檔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}書桌上放著幾乎全新的參考書
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}彷彿是逃避身體的顫抖 立刻帶上了耳機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:11.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}不識的歌手的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}標題不詳的曲目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}剛好流淌進耳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}「想要活下來對吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:20.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}開始嘈雜的世界會場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}如同被波浪拍打一般搖曳的摩天樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}這傢伙真價實的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:27.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}不管怎樣聽  都是早已厭倦的自己的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:29.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}「用20秒越過那座丘陵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:32.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}它的意義  就算不想  你也會知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:35.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}不容懷疑地迴響在耳中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:37.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad3\yshad1}20秒後的未來」
